                poster: 'data:image/jpeg;base64,',

            },
            {

                genre: 'Crime, Drama, Fantasy',
                director: 'Frank Darabont',
                cast: 'Tom Hanks, Michael Clarke Duncan, David Morse',
                plot: 'The lives of guards on Death Row are affected by one of their charges: a black man accused of child murder and rape, yet who has a mysterious gift.',
                poster: 'data:image/jpeg;base64,',

            {
                id: 25,
                title: 'Parasite',
                year: 2019,
                genre: 'Drama, Thriller',
                director: 'Bong Joon Ho',
                cast: 'Song Kang-ho, Lee Sun-kyun, Cho Yeo-jeong',
                plot: 'Greed and class discrimination threaten the newly formed symbiotic relationship between the wealthy Park family and the destitute Kim clan.',
                poster: 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYWZjMjk3ZTItODQ2ZC00NTY5LWE0ZDYtZTI3MjcwN2Q5NTVkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODk4OTc3MTY@._V1_QL75_UX380_CR0,0,380,562_.jpg',
                rating: 8.5,

            }
            // You would continue to add more movies here, up to 100 or more!
            // Remember to adjust the 'id' sequentially.
        ];

        // --- SPA (Single Page Application) Navigation ---
        const pages = document.querySelectorAll('.page');
        const navLinks = document.querySelectorAll('a[data-page]');

        function showPage(pageId) {
            pages.forEach(page => page.classList.remove('active'));
            document.getElementById(pageId).classList.add('active');
            
            navLinks.forEach(link => {
                link.classList.remove('active');
                if (link.getAttribute('data-page') === pageId) {
                    link.classList.add('active');
                }
            });
            window.scrollTo(0, 0);
        }

        navLinks.forEach(link => {
            link.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
                e.preventDefault();
                const pageId = e.target.getAttribute('data-page');
                if (pageId === 'collection') {
                    showCollectionPage();
                } else {
                    showPage(pageId);
                }
            });
        });

        // --- LOCALSTORAGE MANAGEMENT ---
        const getFromLS = (key) => JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(key) || '[]');
        const saveToLS = (key, data) => localStorage.setItem(key, JSON.stringify(data));

        // --- RENDER FUNCTIONS ---
        function renderMovieCards(movieArray, container) {
            if (movieArray.length === 0) {
                container.innerHTML = `<div class="empty-state"><h3>No movies found.</h3><p>Try a different search or add movies to your collection!</p></div>`;
                return;
            }
            container.innerHTML = movieArray.map(movie => `
                <div class="movie-card">
                    <a onclick="showMovieDetail(${movie.id})">
                        <img src="${movie.poster}" alt="${movie.title} Poster" loading="lazy" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/200x300.png?text=No+Image';">
                        <div class="movie-card-content">
                            <h3>${movie.title}</h3>
                            <p>${movie.year} &bull; ${movie.genre}</p>
                            <div class="rating">
                               <span class="star">⭐</span> ${movie.rating}/10
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
            `).join('');
        }

        // --- PAGE-SPECIFIC LOGIC ---
        
        // Render Single Movie Page
        window.showMovieDetail = (movieId) => {
            const movie = movies.find(m => m.id === movieId);
            if (!movie) return;

            const collection = getFromLS('myCollection');
            const isInCollection = collection.includes(movieId);

            const detailContainer = document.getElementById('movie-detail-container');
            detailContainer.innerHTML = `
                <div id="movie-detail-content">
                    <img src="${movie.poster}" alt="${movie.title} Poster" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/300x450.png?text=No+Image';">
                    <div class="movie-info">
                        <h1>${movie.title}</h1>
                        <div class="meta">
                            <span>${movie.year}</span> &bull;
                            <span>Directed by ${movie.director}</span>
                        </div>
                        <p><strong>Genre:</strong> ${movie.genre}</p>
                        <p><strong>Cast:</strong> ${movie.cast}</p>
                        <p><strong>Plot:</strong> ${movie.plot}</p>
                        <button class="btn btn-add" id="collection-btn" onclick="toggleCollection(${movie.id})" ${isInCollection ? 'disabled' : ''}>
                            ${isInCollection ? 'In Your Collection' : 'Add to Collection'}
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="review-section">
                    <h2>Reviews</h2>
                    <div class="initial-review">
                        <div class="review-author">IMDb User</div>
                        <div class="review-rating">${'⭐'.repeat(Math.round(movie.rating/2))} (${movie.rating}/10)</div>
                        <p>${movie.imdb_comment}</p>
                    </div>
                    <div id="reviews-list"></div>
                    <hr>
                    <h3>Write Your Own Review</h3>
                    <form id="review-form">
                        <input type="hidden" id="movie-id-input" value="${movie.id}">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="reviewer-name">Your Name (Optional)</label>
                            <input type="text" id="reviewer-name" placeholder="e.g., Alex R.">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="rating">Rating</label>
                            <select id="rating" required>
                                <option value="5">★★★★★ (Excellent)</option>
                                <option value="4">★★★★☆ (Great)</option>
                                <option value="3">★★★☆☆ (Good)</option>
                                <option value="2">★★☆☆☆ (Fair)</option>
                                <option value="1">★☆☆☆☆ (Poor)</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="review-comment">Your Review</label>
                            <textarea id="review-comment" rows="5" placeholder="Share your thoughts on the movie..." required></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn">Submit Review</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            `;
            
            renderUserReviews(movie.id);
            attachReviewFormListener();
            showPage('single-movie-page');
        }
        
        // Collection Logic
        window.toggleCollection = (movieId) => {
            let collection = getFromLS('myCollection');
            const collectionBtn = document.getElementById('collection-btn');
            if (collection.includes(movieId)) {
                // This case is disabled for now, but could be used to allow removal
            } else {
                collection.push(movieId);
                saveToLS('myCollection', collection);
                collectionBtn.textContent = 'In Your Collection';
                collectionBtn.disabled = true;
            }
        };
        
        function showCollectionPage() {
            const collectionIds = getFromLS('myCollection');
            const collectionMovies = movies.filter(movie => collectionIds.includes(movie.id));
            const collectionGrid = document.getElementById('collection-grid');
            renderMovieCards(collectionMovies, collectionGrid);
            showPage('collection');
        }
        
        // Review Logic
        function renderUserReviews(movieId) {
            const reviewsList = document.getElementById('reviews-list');
            if(!reviewsList) return;
            const userReviews = getFromLS(`reviews_${movieId}`);
            
            if (userReviews.length === 0) {
                reviewsList.innerHTML = '';
                return;
            }
            reviewsList.innerHTML = userReviews.map(review => `
                <div class="review">
                    <h4>${review.name.replace(/</g, "&lt;") || 'Anonymous'}</h4>
                    <p class="review-rating">${'★'.repeat(review.rating)}${'☆'.repeat(5 - review.rating)}</p>
                    <p>${review.comment.replace(/</g, "&lt;")}</p>
                </div>
            `).join('');
        }
        
        function attachReviewFormListener() {
            const reviewForm = document.getElementById('review-form');
            if(reviewForm){
                    reviewForm.addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
                        e.preventDefault();
                        const movieId = document.getElementById('movie-id-input').value;
                        const newReview = {
                            name: document.getElementById('reviewer-name').value,
                            rating: parseInt(document.getElementById('rating').value),
                            comment: document.getElementById('review-comment').value
                        };
                        let userReviews = getFromLS(`reviews_${movieId}`);
                        userReviews.unshift(newReview);
                        saveToLS(`reviews_${movieId}`, userReviews);
                        renderUserReviews(movieId);
                        reviewForm.reset();
                    });
            }
        }

        // --- INITIALIZE PAGES ---

        // Homepage
        const topMoviesGrid = document.getElementById('top-movies-grid');
        renderMovieCards(movies.slice(0, 8), topMoviesGrid); // Feature top 8 movies

        // All Movies Page
        const allMoviesGrid = document.getElementById('all-movies-grid');
        const searchInput = document.getElementById('movie-search');

        renderMovieCards(movies, allMoviesGrid);
        searchInput.addEventListener('input', (e) => {
            const searchTerm = e.target.value.toLowerCase();
            const filteredMovies = movies.filter(movie => 
                movie.title.toLowerCase().includes(searchTerm) ||
                movie.director.toLowerCase().includes(searchTerm) ||
                movie.genre.toLowerCase().includes(searchTerm)
            );
            renderMovieCards(filteredMovies, allMoviesGrid);
        });
        
        showPage('home');
    });
    </script>
